com.i2group.apollo.auditservice.transport

Class AuditResults

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.i2group.apollo.auditservice.transport.AuditResults

  • public final class AuditResults
extends Object
    Contains the AuditEntrys that form the results of a request to the audit service, and an indication of whether the permitted number of results was exceeded.

    2.0
